OL,5, The cross-party body in charge of the  
OL,6, Scottish Parliament has confirmed it   
OL,7, will investigate the health secretary's
OL,8, #11,000 data roaming bill.             
OL,10,FThe charge, initially paid out of the  
OL,11,Fpublic purse, was racked up on Michael 
OL,12,FMatheson's parliamentary iPad during a 
OL,13,Fholiday to Morocco almost a year ago.  
OL,15,FMr Matheson admitted last week that his
OL,16,Fsons had used data from the device to  
OL,17,Fwatch football.                        
OL,19,FHe referred himself to the Scottish    
OL,20,FParliament Corporate Body (SPCB).      
